titles.title: A concurrent resolution commending the Alaska Army National Guard for its service to the State of Alaska and the citizens of the United States.

action.text: Referred to the Committee on Armed Services.

bill.summary:
12/19/2007--Introduced.
Commends the 3rd Battalion, 29th Infantry of the Alaska Army National Guard upon its completion of deployment and service to the Commonwealth of Alaska and the citizens of the United States.
